<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Dancing+Script&family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap');

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background: center / cover no-repeat url(../static/bg2.jpg);
            color: #fff;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        #navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        #navbar ul {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
        }

        #navbar li {
            padding: 10px 20px;
        }

        #navbar li a {
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        #navbar li a:hover {
            color: goldenrod;
        }

        #navbar .logo h1 {
            font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;
            font-size: 30px;
            color: white;
        }

        .rightNav input {
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 20px;
            outline: none;
            transition: width 0.3s;
        }

        .rightNav input:hover {
            width: 200px;
        }

        #introSection {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
        }

        #introSection h1 {
            font-size: 40px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        #contactSection,
        #aboutSection {
            padding: 50px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        #contactSection {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
        }

        .card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 30%;
            margin: 10px;
            display: inline-block;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            transition: transform 0.3s, background 0.3s;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .card h3 {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .card-img img {
            height: 100px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        #aboutSection {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            color: white;
        }

        #aboutSection h1 {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 35px;
        }

        #aboutSection .about-content {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        #aboutSection .about-content p {
            max-width: 800px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        #aboutSection .team {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        #aboutSection .team .member {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 10px;
            width: 200px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

        #aboutSection .team .member:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        #aboutSection .team .member img {
            border-radius: 50%;
            height: 100px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        #footer {
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: black;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 15px;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <nav id="navbar">
        <div class="logo">
            <h1>Quiz</h1>
        </div>
        <ul>
            <li class="home"><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contactSection">Contact Us</a></li>
            <li><a href="#aboutSection">About</a></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="rightNav">
            <input type="text" placeholder="Search here" />
            <ul>
                <li class="rnItem"><a href="/login">Login</a></li>
                <li class="rnItem">|</li>
                <li class="rnItem"><a href="/register">Register</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section id="introSection">
        <h1>Explore as much as you can and</h1>
        <h1>Become best out of the best</h1>
    </section>

    <section id="contactSection">
        <h1>Contact Us</h1>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Quiz Time</h3>
            <div class="card-box">
                <div class="card-img"><img src="../static/Quiz_time.jpg" alt="Quiz_time" /></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Register for Upcoming Quizs</h3>
            <div class="card-box">
                <div class="card-img"><img src="../static/Upcoming_quiz.jpg" alt="Register for Upcoming Quizs" /></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Expert advice</h3>
            <div class="card-box">
                <div class="card-img"><img src="../static/expert.jpg" alt="Expert advice" /></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="aboutSection">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <div class="about-content">
            <p>Welcome to Quiz, the ultimate platform for quiz enthusiasts. Our mission is to create a vibrant community where knowledge seekers can come together to challenge themselves, learn, and grow. Whether you are looking to test your knowledge, prepare for competitive exams, or simply have fun, Quiz has something for everyone.</p>
            <p>Our team is passionate about education and believes in the power of quizzes to enhance learning and retention. We offer a wide range of quizzes across various topics, including science, history, literature, and more. Our quizzes are designed to be both informative and engaging, ensuring that you not only test your knowledge but also learn new facts and concepts along the way.</p>
            <p>Join us on this exciting journey of discovery and improvement. We are committed to providing you with the best quiz experience possible, with regular updates, new quizzes, and exciting features. Thank you for being a part of our community!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team">
            <div class="member">
                <img src="../static/Aatif.png" alt="Team Member 1">
                <h3>MD.Aatif Hasan</h3>
                <p></p>
            </div>
            <div class="member">
                <img src="../static/Nasir.png" alt="Team Member 2">
                <h3>Kaji Nasiruddin Ahmed</h3>
                <p></p>
            </div>
            <div class="member">
                <img src="../static/vishal.jpg" alt="Team Member 3">
                <h3>Vishal Kumar</h3>
                <p></p>
            </div>

            <div class="member">
                <img src="../static/member4.jpg" alt="Team Member 4">
                <h3>Ahsan Habib</h3>
                <p></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer id="footer">
        &copy; 2024 Quiz. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
</body>

</html>
